## 1. Synthesis Request Summary

This document specifies the synthesis of a personalized multi-epitope mRNA vaccine construct encoding **{{ n_epitopes }} tumor-specific neoantigen{{ 's' if n_epitopes != 1 else '' }}** identified from somatic variant calling on patient `{{ sample }}`. The construct is intended for **investigational/research use only** and requires veterinary oncologist sign-off prior to administration.

