## 11. Dosing Guidance

Suggested starting dose range for canine subjects: **1–10 µg / kg body weight**, intramuscular, prime + 2 boosts at 3-week intervals (based on published canine neoantigen vaccine literature). Final dose, route, and schedule **require veterinary oncologist sign-off prior to administration.**

